# Project Telos Third-Wave Closed-Loop Demo

Date: 2026-07-02

Purpose: move from tool-by-tool claims to one compact proof loop: BuildLang emits a policy-pinned compiler receipt, Learn turns that proof packet into a re-verifiable lesson, Build Color supplies a visible measurement lane, and Telos/Crucible preserve the public handoff boundary.

## Verified Loop

| Segment | Evidence | Boundary |
| --- | --- | --- |
| BuildLang policy receipt | `buildlang-hello-ci-review-receipt.json` was generated by `buildc check examples\quickstart\hello.bld --profile ci-review --expect-profile-digest 265584dc495e50171aaa14ab84e0522a34de5b645a703b360c8209068b36f43b --receipt <path>`. `buildc receipt verify <receipt> --source examples\quickstart\hello.bld --expect-profile ci-review --json` returned `status: passed` with 18 passed checks. | Source-checkout demo only. Does not prove full compiler correctness, language replacement, or Build Universe compilation. |
| Proof packet | `buildlang-hello-proof-packet.json` binds only the source file ref/hash and BuildLang receipt ref/hash. | Packet contains refs and hashes, not source bodies. |
| Learn prooflesson | `node C:\dev\public\learn\src\cli.mjs tutor prooflesson buildlang-hello --packet <packet>` wrote `tutor\buildlang-hello.prooflesson.json`; `learn tutor reverify buildlang-hello` returned `VERIFIED`. | Lesson is a study scaffold and retrieval prompt, not an answer dump or credential bypass. |
| Build Color measurement lane | `python -m build_color.cli --version` reports `Build Color v1.0.2`; `info`, `convert`, and `difference` commands produced numeric outputs; `python -m pytest tests -q` passed 458 tests. | Software-side measurement only. No physical meter, display mutation, ICC install, LUT write, or calibration accuracy claim. |
| Telos measurement bridge | `node demo\measurement-layers.mjs --summary` reports 10 layers and 10 measurements with `MATCH`; `node demo\display-calibration.mjs --summary` reports read-only hardware, 3 targets, 4 patch sets, and 5 artifact types; the two focused tests pass. | Read-only proof contract. Hardware mutation remains disabled. |

