## Public Post Angle

> This is the Telos pattern: a compiler receipt becomes a proof packet; the proof packet becomes a learning object; the learning object re-verifies; a visual measurement lane carries numeric evidence; every claim stays bounded by what was actually checked.

## Do Not Post

- "BuildLang replaces Julia today."
- "BuildLang has fully sound linear types."
- "Learn teaches the answer or completes credentials."
- "Build Color calibrated a physical display."
- "Telos proves new physics from this demo."
- "The PATH installs for Learn, BuildLang, or Emet are fixed."
